[{"title":"数学博客开张","url":"/math-notes-blog/posts/634b/","content":"\n这里是记录我数学思考的博客。\n\n以笔记和例题为主，公式用 MathJax 渲染：\n$$\n\\frac{\\partial^2 u}{\\partial t^2} = a^2 \\nabla^2 u\n$$\n\n在这个时代的潮流中，虽然手搓已经失去了效率一说，权威也被解构，那么——\n\n似乎一切的自我陶醉都是一种自作多情，但\n\n又何妨呢？\n\n心中拥有美好，荒岛也能耕种出繁花～\n\n孤芳自赏者，毋为世事倾侧。\n\n主博客请访问 [flowwalker.github.io](https://flowwalker.github.io)。\n","tags":["开篇"],"categories":["站务"]},{"url":"/math-notes-blog/index.html"},{"url":"/math-notes-blog/vercel.json","content":"{\n  \"rewrites\": [\n    { \"source\": \"/math-notes-blog/:path*\", \"destination\": \"/:path*\" }\n  ]\n}\n"},{"title":"关于","url":"/math-notes-blog/about/index.html","content":"\n这里是记录我数学思考的博客。\n\n大学上过学期北大数院的数学分析，或许因此深知自己的天赋不在此，亦或曾经淡化的思维性已经消磨渐去，但不管如何——那时学习不断刷新认知的感觉确实令人enchanted\n\n希望如果有机会，有时间，自己也能够静静地喝上一杯咖啡，安然翻开这片布满繁星的荒野～"},{"title":"四处仙山","url":"/math-notes-blog/links/index.html","content":"\n天涯即比邻。此处为笔者的其他专题仙山之地, 敬请赏玩~\n\n<div class=\"link-card-wrapper\">\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io\" class=\"link-card\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/main-blog-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker的主博客</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">每有会意, 便欣然忘食</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/flowwalker-wiki/\" class=\"link-card\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/wiki-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker的悟道Wiki</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">用 Obsidian + Quartz 编织的知识网络</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/physics-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/physics-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">格物Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">天地一蜉蝣, 可观宙宇阔? 可叹天高地迥</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/coding-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/coding-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">码艺Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">fingers flutter like butterflies over keys</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/engineering-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/engineering-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">工巧Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">于浩歌狂热之际饮冰寒凉 </span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n</div>\n"},{"title":"标签","url":"/math-notes-blog/tags/index.html"},{"title":"分类","url":"/math-notes-blog/categories/index.html"}]